      "role": "user",
      "content": "i feel like im just constantly performing. like every single day is just this exhausting masquerade and i cant keep the mask on anymore. it feels like there's no version of my life where i can just... exist without it being a battle. i'm just so tired of fighting a world that won't let me be me.",
